long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
📢 Open Google Keep in side panel/popup window. Open source

🔔 Top Features
✪ Open Google Keep in side panel/popup window
✪ Free and open source: https://github.com/anilkumarum/sideYT
✪ Don't inject custom script in Google Keep
✪ no tracking, no Ads

✅ No custom script injected
sideKeep don't inject custom script in Google Keep 
Just change layout to fit into sidePanel by using CSS

## How to use sideKeep

Pin sideKeep after install extension
Click on sideKeep or (Ctrl+Shift+K) to open Google Keep  in side Panel
Change side panel -> pop window, go to extension's options page

ℹ️ Support 
Please report issues on github issues https://github.com/anilkumarum/sideKeep/issues
For contact, Please mail us on 📧 webrailhelp@gmail.com
